Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴君  就算你的球被打到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也會在身後保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快投啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我們  相信夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們盡情地做自己力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  無論輸贏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們打一場最漂亮的比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最棒的夥伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉YEAHYEAH  肌肉YEAHYEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:20.72,up,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  和理樹再靠近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是現在能一直持續下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠  持續下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹  你覺得呢
